Modules | Files | Data Structures | Enumerations | Functions
UAVObject set for this firmware
Tau Labs Core components

Modules

 Accels
 The accelerometer sensor data, rotated into body frame.
 
 AccessoryDesired
 Desired Auxillary actuator settings. Comes from ManualControlModule.
 
 ActuatorCommand
 Contains the pulse duration sent to each of the channels. Set by Actuator Module.
 
 ActuatorDesired
 Desired raw, pitch and yaw actuator settings. Comes from either Stabilization Module or ManualControlModule depending on FlightMode.
 
 ActuatorSettings
 Settings for the Actuator Module that controls the channel assignments for the mixer based on AircraftType.
 
 ADCRouting
 Selection of optional hardware configurations.
 
 AirspeedActual
 UAVO for true airspeed, calibrated airspeed, angle of attack, and angle of slip.
 
 AirspeedSettings
 Settings for the BaroAirspeed module used on CopterControl or Revolution.
 
 AltHoldSmoothed
 The output on the kalman filter on altitude.
 
 AltitudeHoldDesired
 Holds the desired altitude (from manual control) as well as the desired attitude to pass through.
 
 AltitudeHoldSettings
 Settings for the AltitudeHold module.
 
 AttitudeActual
 The updated Attitude estimation from AHRSCommsModule.
 
 AttitudeSettings
 Settings for the Attitude module used on CopterControl.
 
 AttitudeSimulated
 The simulated Attitude estimation from Sensor acquisition module.
 
 BaroAirspeed
 The raw data from the dynamic pressure sensor with pressure, temperature and airspeed.
 
 BaroAltitude
 The raw data from the barometric sensor with pressure, temperature and altitude estimate.
 
 CameraDesired
 Desired camera outputs. Comes from CameraStabilization module.
 
 CameraStabSettings
 Settings for the Camera Stabilization Module mmodule.
 
 FaultSettings
 Allows testers to simulate various fault scenarios.
 
 FirmwareIAPObj
 Queries board for SN, model, revision, and sends reset command.
 
 FixedWingAirspeeds
 Settings for the FixedWingPathFollowerModule.
 
 FixedWingPathFollowerSettings
 Settings for the FixedWingPathFollowerModule.
 
 FixedWingPathFollowerSettingsCC
 Settings for the FixedWingPathFollowerModule.
 
 FixedWingPathFollowerStatus
 Object Storing Debugging Information on PID internals.
 
 FlightBatterySettings
 Flight Battery configuration.
 
 FlightBatteryState
 Battery status information.
 
 FlightPlanControl
 Control the flight plan script.
 
 FlightPlanSettings
 Settings for the flight plan module, control the execution of the script.
 
 FlightPlanStatus
 Status of the flight plan script.
 
 FlightStatus
 Contains major flight status information for other modules.
 
 FlightTelemetryStats
 Maintains the telemetry statistics from the OpenPilot flight computer.
 
 GCSReceiver
 A receiver channel group carried over the telemetry link.
 
 GCSTelemetryStats
 The telemetry statistics from the ground computer.
 
 GPSPosition
 Raw GPS data from GPSModule. Should only be used by AHRSCommsModule.
 
 GPSSatellites
 Contains information about the GPS satellites in view from GPSModule.
 
 GPSTime
 Contains the GPS time from GPSModule. Required to compute the world magnetic model correctly when setting the home location.
 
 GPSVelocity
 Raw GPS data from GPSModule.
 
 GroundPathFollowerSettings
 Settings for the GroundPathFollowerModule.
 
 GroundTruth
 Ground truth data output by a simulator.
 
 Gyros
 The rate gyroscope sensor data, in body frame.
 
 GyrosBias
 The online-estimate of gyro bias.
 
 HomeLocation
 HomeLocation setting which contains the constants to tranlate from longitutde and latitude to NED reference frame. Automatically set by GPSModule after acquiring a 3D lock. Used by AHRSCommsModule.
 
 HwCopterControl
 Selection of optional hardware configurations.
 
 HwDiscoveryF4
 Selection of optional hardware configurations.
 
 HwFlyingF3
 Selection of optional hardware configurations.
 
 HwFlyingF4
 Selection of optional hardware configurations.
 
 HwFreedom
 Selection of optional hardware configurations.
 
 HwOSD
 Selection of optional hardware configurations.
 
 HwQuanton
 Selection of optional hardware configurations.
 
 HwRevolution
 Selection of optional hardware configurations.
 
 HwRevoMini
 Selection of optional hardware configurations.
 
 HwSparky
 Selection of optional hardware configurations.
 
 I2CStats
 Tracks statistics on the I2C bus.
 
 I2CVM
 Snapshot of the register and RAM state of the I2C Virtual Machine.
 
 I2CVMUserProgram
 Allows GCS to provide a user-defined program to the I2C Virtual Machine.
 
 INSSettings
 Settings for the INS to control the algorithm and what is updated.
 
 INSState
 Contains the INS state estimate.
 
 MagBias
 The gyro data.
 
 Magnetometer
 The mag data.
 
 ManualControlCommand
 The output from the ManualControlModule which descodes the receiver inputs. Overriden by GCS for fly-by-wire control.
 
 ManualControlSettings
 Settings to indicate how to decode receiver input by ManualControlModule.
 
 MixerSettings
 Settings for the Actuator Module that controls the channel assignments for the mixer based on AircraftType.
 
 MixerStatus
 Status for the matrix mixer showing the output of each mixer after all scaling.
 
 ModuleSettings
 Optional module enable/disable configuration.
 
 NedAccel
 The projection of acceleration in the NED reference frame used by Guidance.
 
 NEDPosition
 Contains the current position relative to HomeLocation.
 
 ObjectPersistence
 Someone who knows please enter this.
 
 OPLinkSettings
 OPLink configurations options.
 
 OPLinkStatus
 OPLink device status.
 
 OsdSettings
 OSD settings used by the OSDgen module.
 
 OveroSyncSettings
 Settings to control the behavior of the overo sync module.
 
 OveroSyncStats
 Maintains statistics on transfer rate to and from over.
 
 PathDesired
 The endpoint or path the craft is trying to achieve. Can come from ManualControl or PathPlanner.
 
 PathPlannerSettings
 Settings for the PathPlanner Module.
 
 PathStatus
 Status of the current path mode Can come from any PathFollower module.
 
 PoiLocation
 Contains the current Point of interest relative to HomeLocation.
 
 PositionActual
 Contains the current position relative to HomeLocation.
 
 RateDesired
 Status for the matrix mixer showing the output of each mixer after all scaling.
 
 ReceiverActivity
 Monitors which receiver channels have been active within the last second.
 
 RelayTuning
 The input to the relay tuning.
 
 RelayTuningSettings
 Setting to run a relay tuning algorithm.
 
 RevoSettings
 Settings for the revo to control the algorithm and what is updated.
 
 SensorSettings
 Settings for the Attitude module.
 
 SonarAltitude
 The raw data from the ultrasound sonar sensor with altitude estimate.
 
 StabilizationDesired
 The desired attitude that Stabilization Module will try and achieve if FlightMode is Stabilized. Comes from ManaulControlModule.
 
 StabilizationSettings
 PID settings used by the Stabilization module to combine the AttitudeActual and AttitudeDesired to compute ActuatorDesired.
 
 StateEstimation
 Settings for how to estimate the state.
 
 StateFilter
 Settings for how to estimate the state.
 
 SystemAlarms
 Alarms from OpenPilot to indicate failure conditions or warnings. Set by various modules.
 
 SystemSettings
 Select airframe type. Currently used by Actuator Module to choose mixing from ActuatorDesired to ActuatorCommand.
 
 SystemStats
 CPU and memory usage from OpenPilot computer.
 
 TabletInfo
 The information from the tablet to the UAVO.
 
 TaskInfo
 Task information.
 
 TxPIDSettings
 Settings used by TxPID optional module to tune PID settings using R/C transmitter.
 
 VelocityActual
 Updated by AHRSCommsModule and used within GuidanceModule for velocity control.
 
 VelocityDesired
 Used within GuidanceModule to communicate between the task computing the desired velocity and the PID loop to achieve it (running at different rates).
 
 VibrationAnalysisOutput
 FFT output from module.
 
 VibrationAnalysisSettings
 Settings for the VibrationTest Module.
 
 VtolPathFollowerSettings
 Settings for the VtolPathFollowerModule.
 
 WatchdogStatus
 For monitoring the flags in the watchdog and especially the bootup flags.
 
 Waypoint
 A waypoint the aircraft can try and hit. Used by the PathPlanner module.
 
 WaypointActive
 Indicates the currently active waypoint.
